@startuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
title What is inside a Cardano treasure chest

package "One chest (a UTXO)" {
  [Coins inside\n(and other tokens too)] as V
  [A label saying who it belongs to] as A
  [A sticky note with extra facts\n(Datum)] as D
}

package "Only shown when you open it" {
  [The note you hand over\n(Redeemer)] as R
  [The whole receipt the guard reads\n(Context)] as C
}

V -[hidden]-> A
A -[hidden]-> D
note bottom of D
  Bitcoin's chest has only coins and a lock.
  Cardano's chest also carries a sticky note.
end note
@enduml
